    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "big part of the DAICO idea was already described by @vbuterin in his ICO methods article [1]\r\n\r\n[1] https://vitalik.ca/general/2017/06/09/sales.html\r\n\r\nwe at @windingtree liked the idea so much, we've implemented it as a part of our token generation event and call it Market Validation Mechanism, feel free to read more [2] about [3] it.\r\n\r\n[2] https://blog.windingtree.com/l%C3%ADf-token-generation-event-f9edb43db739\r\n[3] https://blog.windingtree.com/market-validation-mechanism-in-a-nutshell-ddba1d92be89\r\n\r\nbut most importantly, we have an implementation [4] - we can try to start a work on `DAICO` based on our `MVM`\r\n\r\n[4] https://github.com/windingtree/LifToken/blob/master/contracts/LifMarketValidationMechanism.sol",
